snippet.title: Primordials Legends: Hollow Hero - Official Story and Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn about the story, take a look at the world, and check out gameplay in this trailer for Primordials Legends: Hollow Hero. Get ready to join Brunt, an anthropomorphic wombat, on her journey through the fantasy world of Eridal when this third-person action-adventure game arrives on PC.

Wishlist on Steam now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1727540/Primordials_Legends_Hollow_Hero/
